summary: This header file provides configurations specific to the Cray UNICOS operating system for the Sendmail project. It defines macros indicating that the long long data type is supported and the setitimer system call is not supported on this platform.

logs.reason: This string defines the operating system name and might be used in log messages elsewhere in the codebase to identify the platform.
logs.resolution: This is an informational string used for platform identification, no resolution required.
